om/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/95355273e51d28ee87335ea221974fc5.webm?t=1752778474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/95355273e51d28ee87335ea221974fc5.mp4?t=1752778474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>點頭 = 是 </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>搖頭 = 不是</i> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/abd17870204173d10db070a2a2c5acac.webp?t=1752778474\" width=800 height=2 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/e5dcbd16f32663c7d771b0581efba55f.webp?t=1752778474\" width=24 height=24 /></span>   <strong>控制</strong> <br><br>專為Meta Quest控制器設計，也兼容其他控制器。手部追蹤僅在通過Meta Quest Link的OpenXR版本中支持。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/285b3211ea03c3c6b9500a3dbd98cd83.poster.avif?t=1752778474\" width=546 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/285b3211ea03c3c6b9500a3dbd98cd83.webm?t=1752778474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/285b3211ea03c3c6b9500a3dbd98cd83.mp4?t=1752778474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😳👉👈 <i>= 相機移動</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遺憾的是，<strong>斷臂或無手人士</strong>無法使用所有手勢，但可以使用VR控制器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制是鏡像的，<strong>單手操作</strong>是可能的。另一隻手可以自由使用。只要有一隻手，就可以享受遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/abd17870204173d10db070a2a2c5acac.webp?t=1752778474\" width=800 height=2 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/e5dcbd16f32663c7d771b0581efba55f.webp?t=1752778474\" width=24 height=24 /></span>   特點</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 全語音同步（超過3000個字符）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手部追蹤（僅限Meta Quest）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與玩家動作同步的動畫，或以不同模式自動生成的動畫</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根據您在現實世界中的姿勢（坐著、躺著、站著等）進行的體位</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >互動</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面部動畫</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >射精倒計時</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事模式和自由模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自訂和服裝更改</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無障礙選項</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含互動物件的多個地圖</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用於瞄準訓練的迷你遊戲（附加獎金）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/58330d9e7b667abd29bb10987009b57a.poster.avif?t=1752778474\" width=486 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/58330d9e7b667abd29bb10987009b57a.webm?t=1752778474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/58330d9e7b667abd29bb10987009b57a.mp4?t=1752778474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/3929808b98aee3d96ca1c71b1cf582ed.poster.avif?t=1752778474\" width=482 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004030/extras/3929808b98aee3d96ca